snippet.title: Can We Sing the Darkness to Light (full performance) | Kyle Pederson
snippet.description:
Enjoy this performance of Can We Sing the Darkness to Light by Kyle Pederson, performed by Transept, conducted by Timothy J. Campbell. This work is composed for SATB choir with divisi and piano. 

For a mini-documentary about the piece, please go to https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xpr94jBne6k.

Video production by Brian Gaukel. 

Purchase the music: https://giamusic.com/resource/can-we-sing-the-darkness-to-light-print-ww1736
